      <title>在Mathematica中进行算符运算</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/phys/%E5%9C%A8mathematica%E4%B8%AD%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97/</link>
